      [
        "I think this is something you'll find out eventually, "
      ],
      [
        "so, I better tell you why right now. "
      ],
      [
        "Ever since I was little, my parents really weren’t there for me. "
      ],
      [
        "They were always busy."
      ],
      [
        "Not with work, but with outings and stuff."
      ],
      [
        "I guess they were just too young when they had me, and decided at 9"
